# How to Play Word Bridge

1. Start with the Top Word
[photo-1488590528505-98d2b5aba04b.jpg]
Look at the word at the top of the screen. This is your starting point.

2. Look at the Target Word
[photo-1486312338219-ce68d2c6f44d.jpg]
The word at the bottom is your target. Your goal is to connect these words through similar words.

3. Enter Similar Words
[photo-1649972904349-6e44c42644a7.jpg]
Type words that are similar to the current word. The progress bar shows how close you are to the target.

4. Build Your Chain
[photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158.jpg]
Each word should be similar to both the previous word and lead you closer to the target word.

5. Use Hints if Needed
[photo-1485827404703-89b55fcc595e.jpg]
Click the hint button if you're stuck. It will suggest a word that helps you progress.

6. Complete the Bridge
[photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6.jpg]
Keep adding similar words until you reach the target word. The shorter your chain, the better your score!
